              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="kontakt-icon"><path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"/></svg>
              <span>Pondělí až pátek 7:00 - 15:30<br>mimo pracovní dobu dle dohody</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="kontakt-info-group">
          <h4>Informace</h4>
          <ul class="kontakt-list-items">
            <li>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="kontakt-icon"><path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/></svg>
